!! Package - PGModels

!!! Class - PGHiddenMarkovModel
The class for working with HMMs in ''Polyglot''.

!!!! withTransitions: andEmissions: andStates: andObservations:
This method sets the 4 main parameters of any HMM and returns a HMM.

==Usage== 
[[[
|hmm|
hmm := PGHiddenMarkovModel new.
hmm withTransitions: transitionProbabilities  andEmissions: emissionProbabilities andStates: hiddenStates asSet andObservations: trainTokens asSet.
]]]

This returns a HMM with these 4 main parameters.